            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, chameleon stride APG , perceive cues APG ",
            "description": "</h3>This <i>+2 studded leather armor</i> comes in a number of varieties, each corresponding to a specific type of terrain from the ranger\u2019s favored terrain list. The armor takes on visual characteristics related to that type of terrain (cold <i>stalking </i>armor might be gray and white with a white fur trim, jungle <i>stalking</i> armor could be lush green with vine patterns, and so on) and makes the wearer blend in more naturally with his surroundings. The stalking armor grants the wearer a +5 competence bonus on Stealth and Perception checks attempted while in that specific terrain.",
