            "description": "</h3>The Sargavan government often issues this armor to scouts traveling through the jungle. This <i>+1 expeditious</i><sup>UE</sup> <i>glamered leather armor </i>is colored a deep brown and painted with jungle camouflage. Scouts transform the armor to match the armor style and symbology of communities they visit, and use the <i>expeditious</i><sup>UE</sup> special ability if they find they\u2019re unwelcome. In its true form, the armor grants a +3 competence bonus on Stealth checks. When transformed to fit a culture\u2019s style of dress, it instead grants a +3 competence bonus on Diplomacy checks against people of that culture.",
