            "description": "</h3>The following suit of armor is generally available only to members of the indicated race or ethnicity.<br/><br/>Thanks to the unusually light and fine links of this halfling-made <i>+2 chain shirt</i>, it imposes no armor check penalty and the wearer\u2019s maximum Dexterity bonus is +5. After a melee attack hits the wearer, he can take a 5-foot step as an immediate action, even if he already took a 5-foot step during his turn. Taking such a step does not interfere with the wearer\u2019s movement during his next turn. A suit of <i>mail of sly steps</i> is usually sized for Small creatures.",
