            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, creator must be good, fly ",
            "description": "</h3><i>Celestial plate armor</i> is a sturdier version of the standard <i>celestial armor</i>. This bright silver suit of <i>+3 full plate</i> is remarkably light, and is treated as medium armor. It has a maximum Dexterity bonus of +6, an armor check penalty of \u20133, and an arcane spell failure chance of 20%. It allows the wearer to use fly on command (as the spell) once per day.",
