            "weight": "\u2014",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor , dispel magic ",
            "description": "</h3>This <i>+1 firearm bullet</i> deals no damage but instead dispels one magical effect on the target, as <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=dispel magic\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>dispel magic</i></a> cast by a 5th-level wizard. If the target has multiple magical effects active, the lowest-level effect is targeted.",
