            "weight": "4 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, cure light wounds , inheritor's smite ",
            "description": "</h3>This <i>+1 longsword</i> sheds light as a torch and when drawn emits a shining starburst around the hilt, similar to Iomedae\u2019s holy symbol. Any cure spells or lay on hands effects used to heal the wielder of this blade heal an additional 1 point of damage per die, up to the effect\u2019s normal maximum healing amount. Once per day, the wielder can use <i>inheritor\u2019s smite</i>.",
