            "cl": "3rd",
            "slot": "weapon",
            "price": "7,315 gp",
            "weight": "4 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, shrink item ",
            "description": "</h3>This steel-tined <i>+1 trident </i>can be commanded to lengthen or shorten its haft (or return to its normal length) as a swift action. It is a two-handed reach weapon when extended but cannot be thrown. If shortened, it can be wielded as a light weapon or hurled as a javelin. Feats or class abilities that apply to tridents apply to a <i>fighter\u2019s fork </i>in any form.",
            "cost": "3,815 gp"
