            "price": "8,000 gp",
            "weight": "4 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, magic weapon ",
            "description": "</h3>These Large gauntlets are bulky, and the palms and fingers are studded with wickedly serrated spikes. The wearer gains a +2 bonus on damage rolls with its claw attacks; the wearer adds this bonus damage once for each claw attack used in a rend. The crude construction and thick metal used in the gauntlets make it difficult for the wearer to perform fine manipulation. Consequently, the wearer takes a \u20134 penalty on all Dexterity-based checks involving her hands.",
