            "weight": "10 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor , true strike , undeath to death ",
            "description": "</h3>This brilliant mithral ballista bolt radiates a blinding sheen. Its fletching is made of white and gold feathers.<br/><br/> This <i>+1 light ballista bolt</i> functions as a <a href=\"MagicWeaponsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Slaying Arrow (greater)\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>greater undead slaying arrow</i></a>, except its enchantment is so potent that it deals 50 points of damage even if the saving throw is successful. If the wielder utters the name of his target as the bolt is fired, he gains the benefits of <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=true strike\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>true strike</i></a> on the attack roll.",
