            "weight": "2 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, entangle , telekinesis ",
            "description": "</h3>This <i>+1 bolas</i>, crafted from strands of jungle vine woven into strong cord and weighted with rocks, is favored by the charauka. Ranged trip attacks with a <i>hammertail</i> are made with a +4 enhancement bonus on the CMB check. In addition, if an attack with a <i>hammertail</i> misses its target, the weapon returns as if it had the <i>returning</i> property.",
