            "weight": "2 lbs.",
            "requirements": "Craft Magic Arms and Armor, blur ",
            "description": "</h3>A <i>+1 short sword </i>with a thin, dull gray blade, this weapon provides a +4 bonus on its wielder\u2019s attack and damage rolls when she makes a sneak attack with it.",
