            "description": "</h3>A curved yellow fang juts from the wooden haft of this light pick in place of a metal tip. Though the fang seems fragile, the enchantments on the weapon render it as hard as steel, and the fang evokes some of the powers of the beast from which it came. A chupar pick functions as a <i>+1 light pick of wounding</i>. When the <i>chupar pick </i>scores a critical hit, its wielder is affected by a <i>haste </i>effect for 7 rounds as if targeted by a <i>haste </i>spell. Subsequent critical hits made while the wielder is affected extend the duration of the <i>haste </i>effect but have no additional effect.",
