            "description": "</h3>The head of this <i>+1 warhammer</i> is made from magically treated stone that is as hard as metal. A <i>shatterstone hammer</i> deals double damage against unattended earthen and stone objects, and gains the benefit of being a <i>bane</i> weapon when used against creatures of the earth subtype and constructs made of clay or stone. Once per day on a successful attack made with the hammer, the wielder can cause the target to be slowed (as the <i>slow</i> spell). A DC 14 Will save negates this effect.",
