            "description": "</h3>This bronze <i>+2 scimitar</i> bears an eagle motif on its pommel, and allows the user to soar through the air to deliver his attacks. As a free action, the wielder can fly without having to maintain concentration, as if affected by the <i>fly</i> spell for up to 20 rounds each day, with a +5 bonus on Fly checks. These rounds need not be consecutive. In addition, as long as the scimitar is in hand, the wielder can use <i>feather fall</i> at will.",
