            "description": "</h3>This wide machete is darkly stained with blood. It is treated as a <i>+1 keen short sword</i> that also has a vicious cutting edge, allowing it to deal slashing damage in addition to piercing damage.<br/><br/> The <i>murderer\u2019s machete</i> grants its wielder the ability to move with unnatural grace and speed while stalking potential victims. The wielder gains a +2 competence bonus on Stealth checks and Survival checks to track. In addition, once per day, the wielder can lick the bloodstains on the blade as a standard action to gain the benefits of <i>cruel jaunt</i> (see page 114).",
