            "description": "</h3>The wielder of this elongated triangular prism can cast up to three spells per day for which the spell\u2019s targets must roll three times for their saving throws and take the middle of the three results, as per <i>threefold sight</i>. A <i>lesser rod of the thriceborn</i> can affect spells up to 3rd level, a <i>rod of the thriceborn</i> can affect spells up to 6th level, and a <i>greater rod of the thriceborn</i> can affect spells up to 9th level. A <i>rod of the thriceborn</i> can\u2019t be used in conjunction with metamagic rods or the Persistent Spell feat. "
