            "cost": "32,305 gp",
            "description": "</h3>This ebon rod is so dark it seems to absorb the light around it. The rod functions as a <i>+2 light mace</i>, and allows its wielder to see in darkness as if she had the see in darkness ability (<i>Bestiary 2 </i>301). Three times per day, the wielder can use it to create a <i>deeper darkness </i>effect (caster level 8th). To use this ability, the rod\u2019s wielder must touch the target object, which is a standard action that provokes attacks of opportunity."
