            "description": "</h3>This rod is a simple, unadorned piece of clear crystal that has been magically hardened. The wielder of the rod is under a constant <i>nondetection </i>effect, as the spell. Furthermore, the rod has the following powers. <ul><li>Three times per day on command, the user of the rod can use it to <i>detect thoughts </i>as the spell.</li><li>Once per day as an immediate action, the wielder may determine whether someone is lying to her, as the <i>discern lies </i>spell.</li></ul>"
