            "description": "</h3>Angels crafted the first <i>staff of wings</i> to assist their mortal allies\r during a fiendish invasion onto the Material Plane. Copies have\r since been made by secular crafters. A <i>staff of wings</i> is made of\r light birch and topped with a carved pair of angelic wings made\r out of precious stone. This staff produces flight effects, and the\r wielder gains translucent, illusory wings upon casting them.\r Depending on the alignment and chosen patron of the creator,\r these wings may appear draconic, feathery, or prismatic, or may\r have other celestial features. The staff allows the use of the\r following spells:\r <ul><li><i>Fly</i> (1 charge)\r</li><li><i>Overland flight</i> (2 charges)\r</li><li><i>Mass fly</i> (3 charges)</li></ul>"
