        "description": "</h3>These gauntlets perform according\r to their appearance until the wearer\r finds herself under attack or in a lifeand-\r death situation. At that time,\r the curse is activated. The wearer\r becomes fumble-fingered, with a\r 50% chance each round of dropping anything held in either\r hand. The gauntlets also lower the wearer’s Dexterity score by 2\r points. Once the curse is activated, the gloves can be removed\r only by means of a <i>remove curse</i> spell, a <i>wish</i>, or a <i>miracle</i>."
