        "cost": "2,000 gp",
        "description": "</h3>As a free action, the wearer of this\r brown leather belt can compress\r himself to fit through tight spaces\r as though affected by a squeeze\r spell for up to 10 rounds per day.\r When using the belt’s squeezing\r ability, the wearer gains a +5 circumstance bonus on Escape\r Artist checks. Once per day as a move action, the wearer can\r reduce his size by one step, as the <i>reduce person</i> spell, for 1\r round. These effects can be used simultaneously."
