        "description": "</h3>This silver, bejeweled set of opera glasses is indistinguishable from a regular set, save that when you look through the lenses you gain a +4 competence bonus to Spot checks. When reading lips, you can understand any spoken language as the <i>comprehend languages</i> spell. You can only use a gossip glass to spy on conversations within line of sight and must be able to see people speak in order to read their lips."
