        "description": "</h3>In rocky or mountainous areas, when this stone-gray cloak is\r worn with the hood drawn up around the head, the wearer\r gains a +5 competence bonus on Stealth checks. Once per\r day, the wearer can create an area of fog equivalent to\r <i>obscuring mist</i>."
