        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, good hope , rage , creator must have the bardic performance or raging song class feature",
        "cost": "4,875 gp",
        "description": "</h3>Even after cleaning and mending, this traveler’s cloak appears worn and weathered. For wearers with the bardic performance class feature, it grants the use of raging song as a 4th-level skald by spending rounds of bardic performance. For wearers with the raging song class feature, it grants the use of inspire courage and inspire competence as a 4th-level bard by spending rounds of raging song.<br/><br/> In addition, each <i>poet’s cloak</i> allows its wearer to grant one specific rage power when using raging song in place of his own rage powers (if any). The specific rage power varies by cloak. It must be usable by a 4th-level skald, and can’t have any prerequisites other than level."
