        "cost": "5,500 gp",
        "description": "</h3>Designed to meet the dual needs of the Chelish elite—glamour and subtlety—the <i>cloak of flash and shadow</i> is a magic reversible cloak. When worn one way, the cloak shimmers with heavy gold and silver embroidery against richly colored silk, and grants you a +2 enhancement bonus to Charisma.<br/><br/>When worn inside-out, the matte-black lining seems to absorb light, cloaking you in shadow and giving you a +2 competence bonus on Stealth checks. In this configuration you can cast <i>blur</i> three times per day.<br/><br/>Reversing the cloak’s position is a standard action and requires at least one free hand."
