        "description": "</h3>These decorative bracers are stippled\r with vibrant colors and have various\r tiny bells sewn onto their surface.\r While wearing them, the wearer gains\r a +5 competence bonus on Perform\r checks. Once per day on command,\r the user can gain the benefit of the\r <i>glibness </i>spell."
