        "slot": "none",
        "price": "150 gp",
        "weight": "—",
        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, gentle repose",
        "cost": "75 gp",
        "description": "</h3>When applied to any matter that was\r once alive, such as wood, paper, or a\r dead body, this ointment allows that\r substance to resist the passage of\r time. Each year of actual time affects\r the substance as if only a day had\r passed. The coated object gains a +1 resistance bonus on all\r saving throws. The unguent never wears off, although it can\r be magically removed (by dispelling the effect, for instance).\r One flask contains enough material to coat eight Medium\r or smaller objects. A Large object counts as two Medium\r objects, and a Huge object counts as four Medium objects."
