        "cost": "300 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This small token is a thumb-sized cylinder of unbreakable greenish glass. A <i>Spire transport token </i>allows the bearer to use the Emerald Spire’s transport function. The bearer can teleport to a level only if she knows and speaks its identifying rune."
