        "price": "750 gp",
        "weight": "3 lbs.",
        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, hostile levitation UC , snare",
        "cost": "375 gp",
        "description": "</h3>Once the command word is\r spoken, this steel disc burrows 3\r inches into the ground. To find it,\r a character with the trapfinding\r ability must succeed at a DC 25 Perception check. Planting the\r mine is a full-round action that provokes attacks of opportunity.<br/><br/>\r Once the mine is set, any creature that steps into its square must\r succeed at a DC 14 Will save or the mine levitates the creature 5\r inches above the ground. A levitated creature can attack but not\r move, is denied its Dexterity bonus to AC, and takes a –4 penalty\r to CMD against bull rush, drag, and reposition combat maneuvers.\r Flying creatures are immune. The creature can attempt a new\r save each round to end the effect. The effect ends after 5 rounds,\r with a successful DC 25 Disable Device check, or with a successful\r saving throw. The land mine is destroyed when the effect ends."
