        "cost": "175 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This longsword glows and has an aura,\r making it appear valuable. Its grip is\r hollow and can be filled with a dose of\r poison (bought separately, and requiring\r a full-round action to refill and rearm).\r Once the sword is grasped, its mechanical\r trap engages: Small needles in the grip\r deliver the poison. Detecting the trap requires a successful DC 30\r Perception check made by a character with the trapfinding ability,\r and disabling it requires a successful DC 28 Disable Device check."
