        "description": "</h3>This multicolored, sturdy glass bead is an aid to members\r of the alchemist class. Once per day on command, a <i>boro\r bead</i> enables the bearer to recharge any one extract that he\r had mixed and then consumed that day. The extract is then\r reconstituted and usable again, just as if it had not been\r drank. The extract must be of a particular level, depending\r on the bead. Different beads exist for recalling one extract\r per day of each level from 1st through 6th. A bead works\r on an infusion, but not a potion, elixir, bomb, mutagen, or\r nonmagical alchemical material such as antitoxin."
