        "description": "</h3>This delicate tin music box can\r produce a great volume of noise\r at a specific time determined by\r its owner. Four command words\r determine what sorts of sounds it\r is to play (battle, fire, massacre,\r or riot), and a fifth determines the delay (anywhere from 1\r round to 20 minutes) until the box begins to produce the desired\r sound. The noise from the box is as loud as 40 people. The sound\r persists for 2d6 rounds."
