        "description": "</h3>Created by the masters within the Kusari-Gama faction, this thumbnail-sized crystal stores a single point of <i>ki</i>. Any person with the <i>ki</i> pool ability may expend the stored <i>ki</i> as if using his own <i>ki</i>. Once the <i>ki</i> is expended, the crystal shatters. In Minkai, the Kusari-Gama monks sometimes craft <i>ki crystals</i> into the hilts of powerful weapons. In Vudra, such crystals are often embedded in small animal statuettes or in shrines venerating a favored deity."
