        "aura": "faint transmutation",
        "cl": "3rd",
        "slot": "none",
        "price": "2,000 gp",
        "weight": "1 lb.",
        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, pyrotechnics , spark ( Advanced Player's Guide )",
        "cost": "1,000 gp (Normal), 2,250 gp (Greater)",
        "description": "</h3>This small crude-looking drum is attached to a strap long enough\r to loop around the wearer’s neck. A successful DC 12 Perform\r (percussion) check activates the drum, which enhances any\r nearby natural or magical fire as long as the bearer spends a\r move action each round to continue playing. All fires (including\r fire spells and effects) within 30 feet of the bearer deal an\r additional 1 point of fire damage (or 2 points for the greater version).<br/><br/>\r All unattended flammable alchemical objects such as\r tindertwigs, flasks of oil or alchemist’s fire, and fireworks within\r this range have a 10% chance of spontaneously igniting or\r exploding (as appropriate to the item) when the drum activates.\r This chance increases by 5% each round and is checked at the\r start of the performer’s turn as long as the playing continues.<br/><br/>\r A <i>greater goblin fire drum</i> has all the above abilities and can\r <i>create pyrotechnics</i> once per day."
