        "description": "</h3>Once the command word is spoken, this 5-foot-diameter loop\r of wire blends with its surroundings. To find it, a character with\r the trapfinding ability must succeed at a DC 30 Perception check.\r Setting the snare is a full-round action that provokes attacks of\r opportunity. Any creature that steps into the snare must succeed\r at a DC 26 Will save or become magically paralyzed, as the spell\r <i>hold monster</i>. This effect can be ended by uttering the command\r word, succeeding at a DC 30 Disable Device check, or succeeding\r at the Will save. The snare is destroyed when the effect ends."
