        "description": "</h3>This jewel-like lens slowly changes colors over time, with no discernible pattern. It may appear as a ruby one morning and a sapphire that night, only to become opaline for the entire next day. Most owners set their <i>rhombocrystal</i> in a metal festoon on a chain and carry it as a pendant, monocle, or loupe. A <i>rhombocrystal</i> can be used as a magnifying glass, and grants its bearer a +5 competence bonus on Appraise checks involving gems and crystals.<br/><br/> If Nivi Rhombodazzle is the bearer’s patron, the bearer gains a +1 luck bonus on Reflex saving throws."
