        "description": "</h3>This malevolent-looking doll is made out of cheap rags and\r embroidery thread and is stuffed with straw or sawdust. A\r creature holding or carrying the doll takes a –4 penalty on\r saving throws against witch hexes. Alternatively, if the doll is\r stuffed with the hair of a creature, any witch holding the doll\r increases the DC of her hexes by +2 when using the hexes\r against that creature. A doll used in this way does not cause\r the witch to take a penalty on her saving throws."
