        "description": "</h3>Once per day, an alchemist can use this simple-looking glass\r vial to combine two extracts into one usable extract as if he\r had the combine extracts discovery. An <i>admixture vial</i> can\r combine extracts of 3rd level or lower. Extracts combined with\r an <i>admixture vial</i> cannot be combined again using this item or\r the combine extracts discovery."
