        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, passwall",
        "cost": "2,500 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This iron gargoyle face holds an iron ring in its mouth. Once\r per day, when the flat back of the gargoyle face is placed\r against a wall, floor, or ceiling, it fuses into place, creating\r a usable door and penetrating the space beyond up to 1\r foot as if using <i>passwall</i>. Speaking the command word\r again ends the <i>passwall </i>effect, returns the surface to its\r previous doorless shape, and releases the doorknocker from\r the surface."
