        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, clairaudience/ clairvoyance",
        "cost": "3,700 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This telescoping brass spyglass functions as a normal spyglass and allows clear vision to the horizon 3 miles away at sea level. From atop a typical crow’s nest or 70-foot-tall tower like Tidewater Rock, this vision extends to over 10 miles. Once per day, the user of a <i>farglass </i>can activate a <i>clairaudience/ clairvoyance </i>effect upon any location seen through the <i>farglass’s </i>lens. As long as the location is kept in sight through the lens, the <i>clairaudience/clairvoyance </i>sensor can move with the location. This effect lasts for up to 5 minutes."
