        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, animate dead",
        "cost": "3,500 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This bottle is crafted from the darkest ebony. When opened\r and held upright, faint whispers can be heard emanating from\r the bottle’s mouth. The bottle initially has 4 charges. When\r turned upside down, the bottle summons a shadow to do the\r bidding of the user, draining 1 charge each round of service.\r As a standard action, the bearer may dismiss the summoned\r shadow. If the shadow kills a humanoid creature of at least\r 4 HD, the bottle gains 1 charge. The bottle is automatically\r restored to 4 charges at sundown."
