        "description": "</h3>This elaborate fan is made with a dozen black feathers set into a metal handle embossed with a stylized crest. The bearer can use it to create a <i>gust of wind</i>, <i>whispering wind</i>, or <i>wind wall</i>. The fan’s effects can be used 3 times per day, in any combination."
