        "cost": "5,000 gp",
        "description": "</h3>Made from bone and sun-dried sinew, this masterwork harp\r produces a vague sense of unease in anyone near it. If the\r owner of this item has the bardic performance class feature\r he can use it to perform a dirge of doom even if he is not of\r sufficient level to normally have access to that ability. A bard\r who can use dirge of doom and who plays the harp as part of\r his performance increases the effective radius to 60 feet."
