        "description": "</h3>Six inches in diameter, one side of this porcelain seal shows a\r many-keyholed padlock, while the other displays a lightning bolt\r superimposed on an open hand. The padlock side is used to lock\r and alarm doors, chests, and other portals. The bearer may speak\r a command word to activate it when holding it against a lockable\r item. If the padlock side of the seal is touching the item, it\r bestows an <i>alarm </i>(mental alarm) and <i>arcane lock</i> on the target\r item. If the lightning bolt side of the seal is touching the item, it\r casts<i> fire trap</i> on the lock (the seal must be held to the lock for 10\r minutes to use this ability).\r<br/><br/>A creature carrying the seal can speak a command word to\r suspend its effects on an item for 1 minute. This ability is usable\r at will, but only works on effects created by that specific seal.\r<br/><br/>The seal can be used at will but can only maintain effects\r on three items at any given time. Using it on a fourth item\r automatically negates the oldest effect."
