        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, fabricate",
        "cost": "6,500 gp",
        "description": "</h3>This magical instrument is usually made of\r gold and inlaid with numerous gems. If the\r proper chords are struck, a single use of\r this lyre negates any attacks made against\r inanimate construction (walls, roof, floor,\r and so on) within 300 feet. This includes the\r effects of a <i>horn of blasting</i>, a <i>disintegrate</i>\r spell, or an attack from a ram or similar siege\r weapon. The lyre can be used in this way\r once per day, with the protection lasting for 30 minutes.\r<br/><br/>The lyre is also useful with respect to building. Once a\r week, its strings can be strummed so as to produce chords\r that magically construct buildings, mines, tunnels, ditches,\r etc. The effect produced in 30 minutes of playing is equal\r to the work of 100 humans laboring for 3 days. Each hour\r after the first, a character playing the lyre must make a DC 18 Perform (string instruments) check. If she fails, she must\r stop and cannot play the lyre again for this purpose until a\r week has passed."
