        "description": "</h3>This long tapering pennant resembles\r a stylized serpentine figure wearing\r a shimmering crown. The figure’s\r claws function as clasps, attaching it\r to a lance, polearm, frame, or staff.\r The pennant has no effect when not\r mounted properly, or when activated\r by a lawfully aligned creature.\r<br/><br/>Planting the pennant in the ground\r generates an area of twisted space\r around the flag out to a range of 30 feet. Any creature that\r teleports into or out of this area is nauseated for 1 round (a\r DC 18 Fortitude save reduces this penalty to sickened). Any creature may end the effect by uprooting the pennant as a\r standard action. The pennant functions for 10 rounds per day.\r These rounds do not need to be consecutive."
