        "description": "</h3>This <i>wayfinder </i>is made of magically\r hardened glass, through which the\r complex inner matrix of the compass\r can be seen. Once per day, the\r wielder of a <i>wayfinder of the planes</i>\r can choose one of the following\r alignments: chaotic, evil, good, or\r lawful. For 1 hour thereafter, the <i>wayfinder of the planes</i> creates\r a <i>magic circle</i> effect against the chosen alignment, centered on\r the <i>wayfinder</i>. Once selected, the alignment of the <i>magic circle</i>\r effect can’t be changed until the effect recharges the next day."
