        "description": "</h3>Favored by Pathfinders exploring dark and dangerous locales, the exterior of this <i>wayfinder</i> is constructed of panels of darkwood with ebony inlays. The panels slide apart to reveal platinum meshwork capable of holding one or two ioun stones. An <i>ebon wayfinder</i> grants the bearer darkvision with a range of 60 feet, and with a command word it can create <i>darkness</i> (as per the spell) once per day, centered on itself.<br/><br/> When one ioun stone is slotted into the device, its <i>darkness</i> ability no longer functions. When a second stone is placed in it, the darkvision ability no longer functions."
