        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, animate dead , spike growth",
        "cost": "11,000 gp",
        "description": "</h3><i>Spikebones</i> are a collection of bleached humanoid bones— typically the ribs, vertebrae, and finger bones—carried in a crude pouch made of the humanoid’s skin and connective tissue. Three times per day, the <i>spikebones </i>can be cast upon the ground as a standard action to create an area of dangerous spikes. Bony in color and shape, these sharp protrusions function like a <i>spike growth </i>spell. The spikes fill four contiguous 10-foot-square areas, shaped by the user at the time of deployment. The spikes remain effective for up to 3 hours, after which they vanish and the <i>spikebones </i>magically reappearing in their pouch."
