        "cost": "15,000 gp",
        "description": "</h3>These drums are kettle drums (hemispheres\r about 1-1/2 feet in diameter on stands).\r They come in pairs and are unremarkable in\r appearance. If both of the pair are sounded,\r all creatures within 120 feet (with the\r exception of those within a 20-foot-radius\r safe zone around the drums) are affected as\r by a <i>fear </i>spell (Will DC 16 partial). <i>Drums of panic</i> can be used\r once per day."
