        "weight": "—",
        "requirements": "Craft Wondrous Item, Maximize Spell, cure light wounds , cure moderate wounds , heal",
        "cost": "17,825 gp, 1,426 XP",
        "description": "</h3>This beautiful watercolor painting depicts a clear mountain stream flanked by moss-covered stones and dew-drenched ferns. Mountains rise up in the background, casting rippled shadows across the water's surface. The silver frame is etched with symbols of healing.<br/><br/>By touching the painting while uttering one of three seperate command words, you may cast the following spells: 3/day - maximized <i>cure light wounds</i> (13 points); 1/day - maximized <i>cure moderate wounds</i> (26 points); 1/week - <i>heal</i>."
