        "description": "</h3>This item is typically fashioned of brass or\r bronze, with a lead stopper bearing special\r seals. Periodically, a thin stream of bittersmelling\r smoke issues from the bottle’s\r top. The bottle can be opened once per\r day. When opened, the efreeti imprisoned\r within issues from the bottle instantly amid\r a cloud of noxious smoke. There is a 10%\r chance (01–10 on d%) that the efreeti is\r insane and attacks immediately upon being\r released. There is also a 10% chance (91–100) that the efreeti\r of the bottle grants three wishes. In either case, afterward the\r efreeti disappears forever, and the bottle becomes nonmagical.\r The other 80% of the time (11–90), the inhabitant of the bottle\r loyally serves the character for up to 10 minutes per day (or until\r the efreeti’s death), doing as she commands. Roll each day the\r bottle is opened for that day’s effect."
